        "Daniel 9:25-26 gives a precise mathematical timeline from the decree to rebuild Jerusalem to 'Messiah the Prince' — a calculation that points to the era of Jesus' triumphal entry and cuts off before the Temple's AD 70 destruction, making a later 'Messiah' candidate impossible.",
