      obedienceLink: "The Sermon on the Mount raises the standard of obedience from behaviour to motivation. Jesus is not satisfied with a cleaned-up exterior — He wants a transformed interior. This is either the most crushing demand ever made, or the most liberating one: it tells you that God sees through performance and wants the real thing. And He provides it — not through your effort but through His Spirit.",
