    title: "Who Is Jesus? The Great Confession",
    bibleRef: "Matthew 16:13-20, John 14:6, Colossians 1:15-20",
    keyVerse: "Simon Peter answered and said, Thou art the Christ, the Son of the living God. — Matthew 16:16",
