      conclusion: "The Holy Spirit's presence is not always dramatic or emotional. It is often quiet, persistent, and most visible in transformation over time. The question is not 'Have I had an emotional experience?' but 'Am I growing in Christ's character? Is Scripture becoming clearer? Am I finding courage I didn't have before?' These are the Spirit's fingerprints.",
